                <h1>Top Tap Dance Techniques: Rhythmic Moves & Styles</h1>
                <p>Tap dance is a vibrant and rhythmic dance form characterized by the use of metal-tipped shoes that create rhythmic sounds on the floor. Originating from African American communities, it combines elements of African dance, Irish jigs, and English clog dancing. This dynamic art form emphasizes musicality, style, and intricate footwork.</p>
